Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: Why didn’t Kamala make this speech four years ago? It’s too late! She has damaged our Country beyond recognition. There is no excuse for what she has done. She is guilty of CRIMES! Now she is begging for forgiveness, but our Country will never forgive her for this GROSS INCOMPETENCE at the Border. ONLY I CAN FIX IT. MAKE AMERICA GREAT AGAIN!
